冰岛议会议员和WikiLeaks组织者Birgitta Jonsdottir<a href="http://news.slashdot.org/story/10/09/06/1827240/WikiLeaks-Calls-For-Assange-To-Step-Down">呼吁WikiLeaks创始人Julian Assange辞职</a>，以专注于澄清他访问瑞典期间发生的<a href="__SLASHLINK__" sect="internet" sid="10/08/21/1424254" sn="article" tid="87">强奸指控</a>。<i>
